vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and (1) an ordinance granting an R-5(A) Single Family District; and (2) an ordinance granting the termination of a D Liquor Control Overlay on property zoned an LO-1 Limited Office District with a D Liquor Control Overlay and an MF-2(A) Multifamily District, on the east side of Homer Street between North Garrett Avenue and North Henderson Avenue
Recommendation of Staff:  Approval of (1) an R-5(A) Single Family District; and (2) approval of the termination of a D Liquor Control Overlay
Recommendation of CPC:  Approval of (1) an R-5(A) Single Family District; and (2) approval of the termination of a D Liquor Control Overlay
Z223-316(LC)
